reviewText: Laughter anytime and all in one package.
My girlfriend loves :Sweet November"... this item scored me some huge points with her.  Kinda a sad movie though.  The other movies aren't bad either and you cant beat the price.
Five stars for "Music & Lyrics" and "Sweet November", Four stars for "Rumor Has It", and "Lucky You" (though I'm still a little curious why "Lucky You" was chosen for inclusion in this collection)...

The DVD's look very different from other DVD's on 4 film favorite series. I have many 4 film favorite and I Love the series but this one came with 2 DVD's without any DVD sticker on them like its a pirated stuff....The movie names are written around the middle ring in extremely small letters. I don't know if its pirated but movies are there so I gave 2 stars otherwise this product is not worth even 1 star.
I love these movies and was very happy to see that they were all together for a great price. I received them sooner than expected and have enjoyed watching them.

The DVD set is good quality, but with any movie it really comes down to personal taste, however some things are common - decent storylines (mostly boy meets girl here) decent acting and quality directing. These films certainly have all these qualities, sadly they don't all appear in one single movie together, the fact that probably contributed to none of them being blockbusters. However, that said, at the price point, certainly entertainment on (4) rainy afternoons with a bowl of ice-cream.
great movie and a good price
Received this on time.  All dvds were in perfect condition.  Very pleased with the order.  Thanks!
I was not disappointed with this DVD, at all. Every film is good. My favorite one  is Sweet November with Charlize Theron and Keanu Reeves.
